data.description: Check out this wonderful property and the many uses this ranch style home on 1.26 acres just outside of Burley City limits on its own well and septic has to offer. The property offers mature landscaping, a Gala Apple tree, Granny Smith Apple trees, three plum trees, one pear tree, and an English walnut tree.  This  home can be a single family home with 5 bedrooms & 2.5 bathrooms, a single family home with a mother-in-law quarter in the basement, OR two rental units. The basement offers its own entrance, 2 bedrooms, a fully renovated bathroom, and a kitchen. On top of that, this property is zone C-2, offering the possibility of adding more rental units, Retail space, Restaurant, Office space, Automobile service stations, Public garages, Service establishments, Mini Storages, and much more. Call today to schedule a showing or to request a list of permitted uses on this  property.
